{"tid":1393171,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【超突發】將於八月十五重設所有會員密碼【fact checked】","createTime":"2019-08-01T04:04:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T04:14:46.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"43b2300959b990865468f435faf7ad3131a743c0","tid":1393171,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:04:42.000Z","msg":"如果八月十五前高登會員冇改既話高登就會自動重設密碼，新密碼會寄去主副電郵。<br />\r\n<span style=\"color: red;\">八月十五前高登所有登入亦會同時失效，所有高登會員亦需重新登入一次。</span><br />\r\n各位高登會員請在八月十五日前更改一次密碼，同時確保副電郵可用，日後作忘記密碼之用。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n更改密碼link<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.hkgolden.com/members/imember_changepw.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkgolden.com%2Fmembers%2Fimember_changepw.aspx&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5x6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=d25b8397\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkgolden.com/members/imember_changepw.aspx</a><br />\r\n或者用newweb登入後於&quot;個人資料&quot;更改<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/01/hkCMPI.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F01%2FhkCMPI.png&h=f828e155&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n如有任何更改密碼困難請到聯絡我們尋求協助。<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/contactus.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fcontactus.aspx&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5x6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=7f255454\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/contactus.aspx</a><br />\r\n如要更改副電郵可附上任何申請帳號時填的資料(登入email, 電話, 部分密碼等等) 及要更改的電郵地址，核對後會更改為新副電郵。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">睇下爭唔爭取到有改密碼既人可以升高級會員/重抽頭像啦</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=7092923&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D7092923%26page%3D1&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5x6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=c95c1bdf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=7092923&amp;page=1</a>"},{"pid":"69c45076e8a8740c0de05038d22274ca83a65083","tid":1393171,"uid":259530,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:05:43.000Z","msg":"黎得連登,都唔會去高登留言啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"994b6640576586306012537fce51a90efe3527df","tid":1393171,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:05:50.000Z","msg":"提示:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n高登好多isp email成廿年曆史<br />\r\n你send去搵鬼收"},{"pid":"0b9683793fcf4c125df84861911e3d59049712de","tid":1393171,"uid":133519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:06:36.000Z","msg":"高登=亞視"},{"pid":"c7ed98c7331ff5391a2687115b180b7a8b74f667","tid":1393171,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:07:37.000Z","msg":"話時話做咩要改密碼？阿祖被人攪緊定點？"},{"pid":"d737e83dccdc10f4473fa689876acc5b778bb8b4","tid":1393171,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:10:11.000Z","msg":"無神神咁搞法有批唔係成日上既會員實奶野上唔番黎"},{"pid":"faf1d56abbcc8e84073e4ea7050599fa4c7f260a","tid":1393171,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:14:46.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n8月2日 公務員罷工集會<br />\n8月5日 一齊罷工 7區集會"}]}